msgid ""
"Previously, you enabled Istio on a single microservice, ``productpage``. "
"You can proceed to enable Istio on the microservices incrementally to get"
" the Istio functionality for more microservices. For the purpose of this "
"tutorial, you will enable Istio on all the remaining microservices in one"
" step."
msgstr ""

